{"tid":1146653,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果中國象棋變成抽卡類手機GAME, 你估會變成點?","createTime":"2019-05-09T10:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T10:13:55.000Z","uid":210745,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"47cad9b7077b6d8496912b69c9798e2f6ad1de5e","tid":1146653,"uid":210745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:58:11.000Z","msg":"王, 車, 馬, 炮, 士, 象, 卒<br />\nD職階變晒抽卡<br />\n每個職階都有D R, SR, SSR卡<br />\n<br />\nD卡除左可以好似正常中國象棋咁移動之外<br />\n唔同既卡仲可以有主動技能或被動技能<br />\n好似車可以2回行動, 馬可以直線衝鋒之類<br />\n將軍可以根據課金程度增加移動範圍<br />\n<br />\n課金可以買D新棋盤<br />\n地圖變大<br />\n甚至某D地圖可以2打2或者增加減少初始佈陣棋子數目 (如4隻馬, 4隻炮)<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 鳩吹無難度"},{"pid":"41d7400ce57c6e7e06ddcf6a47e7267038ef1c7f","tid":1146653,"uid":78907,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:01:01.000Z","msg":"Ok 新start up idea, 師兄我地起啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16f30c6169c5456082d9cafdbb12bf00f6dcfd0","tid":1146653,"uid":81094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:03:54.000Z","msg":"FGO象棋版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"082cad12d0c28d53c37ca3f257aab3cec4c01652","tid":1146653,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:07:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c109cd0fdd9b8b9a4d6e5ab1a6d93abdbe28de71","tid":1146653,"uid":61084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:25:22.000Z","msg":"會變鳩game<br />\n遊戲平衡呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271a683d864e469923774208cccd25131630ee03","tid":1146653,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"無乜市場<br />\n老人家唔玩"},{"pid":"37601be361cdc6832c316f9525c423acefc77887","tid":1146653,"uid":220431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"女體化先"},{"p